Isingeniso kanye nethiyori yomshini ohlanzekile we-aqua: Isitayela sokuqala emhlabeni ngokusebenzisa i-micro-nano bubble yedivayisi yamandla encane ubuchwepheshe obunelungelo lobunikazi, kusetshenziswa ithiyori yokushayisana izikhathi ezingama-299,000 ngesekhondi izakhi ze-high-frequency wave oscillation, khiqiza ama-molecule amanzi aqhume abe yi-watermolecule enomoya-mpilo omkhulu. , bese isikwa i-ultra-high frequency wave, ama-molecule wamanzi e-nano, akhiqiza ama-ion angalungile, i-ultrasound, nama-molecule amanzi anano-high aqukethe umoya-mpilo.Ngena ngokushesha ezimbotsheni zesikhumba, khipha umzimba omdala onezimpondo, ukuhlanza okujulile, isikhumba futhi wandise umoya-mpilo egazini, futhi ukhuthaze umzimba & nokujikeleza kwegazi, wenze kusebenze ukulungiswa kwamaseli, ukubambezeleka kokuguga kwesikhumba, ukudonsa okuhlangene, ukushwabana neminye imiphumela.

'Akumele babe ngabeSatawu abanodlame' 2012-10-09 14:01 Cape Town - Abashayeli bamaloli abanodlame futhi abanesandla ekufeni komshayeli waseKapa, baphumile esandleni futhi abahambisi ngokwemigomo yenyunyana, kumele babahekane nengalo yomthetho, kusho iSA Trade Transport Workers Union. "Asicabangi ukuthi abantu abanjalo bayingxenye yentando yeningi esihambisa ngayo, akusibo abeSatawu," kusho umkhulumeli wenyunyana uVincent Masoga. Umshayeli weloli uGary Stewart, 41, wajikijelwa ngetshe eselolini, ubexhunywe imishini emsiza ukuba akwazi ukuphefumula, kulandela ukuthi elimale kambi ekhanda, wase efelwa wumqondo. Isitimela sezingane sangaphandle esisikhiqizayo siyisitimela esiklanyelwe izingane ngokukhethekile. Isitimela asiphephile nje kuphela, kodwa futhi sinezinhlobonhlobo zezindikimba. Ezinganeni, into yokuqala ezihehayo wukubukeka kohambo lwesitimela, okuyindikimba yesitimela. Amatimu ahlukahlukene angaheha izingane kakhulu. Into yokuqala abazali okufanele bayicabangele ukuthi ukugibela kwezingane ngaphandle kwesitimela kuphephile yini. Ezinganeni ezincane ezingenakho ukuqwashisa ngokuphepha, lapho zithatha uhambo lwesitimela, into ebaluleke kakhulu ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kwazo. Ngale njongo, siklame ngokukhethekile amabhande aphephile, angengezwa ohambweni lwesitimela lwangaphandle oluthengiswa e-Dinis. Uma ufuna ukuphepha okwengeziwe kwezingane isitimela sangaphandle, ungakhetha ukwengeza amabhande aphephile. Sikholelwa ukuthi isitimela sangaphandle esinosayizi wengane esithengiswayo e-Dinis siyisinqumo sakho esingcono kakhulu.
